dfischer.utils

Class ExternalParamFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap
        • dfischer.utils.ExternalParamFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map

    public class ExternalParamFile
extends java.util.HashMap
    External parameter file for very big CGI or HTML-form parameter (greater than 16KB) which is mapped by a hash table.
    Entries inside the external parameter file are formatted as <name>=<value>. Truncating white spaces is not supported.
    Comments can be marked by using a '#' character at the start of a line. Empty lines are skipped.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
